<subSubSection id="C349A3FD211BAE0DFF2D9ADBCC26983D" pageId="6" pageNumber="421" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="8BECF076211BAE0DFF2D9ADBCC26983D" blockId="6.[151,1437,151,825]" pageId="6" pageNumber="421">
<emphasis id="B9272C64211BAE0DFF2D9ADBC90699F4" bold="true" box="[199,335,726,752]" pageId="6" pageNumber="421">Comments.</emphasis>
<taxonomicName id="4C538BF5211BAE0DFEB19ADACAC699F4" authorityName="Townes" authorityYear="1966" box="[347,655,727,752]" class="Insecta" family="Ichneumonidae" genus="Hymenoepimecis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="421" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="cameroni">
<emphasis id="B9272C64211BAE0DFEB19ADACAC699F4" box="[347,655,727,752]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="421">Hymenoepimecis cameroni</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
closely resembles 
<taxonomicName id="4C538BF5211BAE0DFC9B9ADACC8A99F5" authority="Gauld, 2000" authorityName="Gauld" authorityYear="2000" box="[881,1219,727,753]" class="Insecta" family="Ichneumonidae" genus="Hymenoepimecis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="421" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="argyraphaga">
<emphasis id="B9272C64211BAE0DFC9B9ADACC6199F5" box="[881,1064,727,753]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="421">H. argyraphaga</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="EFC28D87211BAE0DFBDE9ADACC8A99F5" author="Gauld, I. D." box="[1076,1219,727,753]" pageId="6" pageNumber="421" pagination="213 - 219" refId="ref6537" refString="Gauld, I. D. (2000) The Re-definition of Pimplinae Genus Hymenoepimecis (Hymenoptera: Ichneumonidae) with a Description of a Plesiomorphic New Costa Rican Species. Journal of Hymenoptera Research, 9 (2), 213 - 219." type="journal article" year="2000">Gauld, 2000</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
mainly by having blackish wings and present epicnemial carina, but differs from it by having absent submetapleural carina (present, extending at least 0.5 of length of pleuron or more or less complete in 
<taxonomicName id="4C538BF5211BAE0DFC419B12CC17983D" authorityName="Gauld" authorityYear="2000" box="[939,1118,799,825]" class="Insecta" family="Ichneumonidae" genus="Hymenoepimecis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="421" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="argyraphaga">
<emphasis id="B9272C64211BAE0DFC419B12CC17983D" box="[939,1118,799,825]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="421">H. argyraphaga</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
).
</paragraph>
